<title>USA: Pegasystems preliminary Q4 shr higher.</title>
<headline>Pegasystems preliminary Q4 shr higher.</headline>
<dateline>CAMBRIDGE, Mass 1997-01-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Pegasystems Inc said Thursday preliminary figures showed earnings for the fourth-quarter were $0.14 a share against $0.06 in the same year-earlier period.  </p>
<p>The company, which develops customer service computer software for banks and other institutions, said the figures also showed earnings for the full year at $0.28 a share against $0.11.</p>
<p>It said an audit had yet to be completed in order to confirm the figures.</p>
